name: Visible Thoughts: 012
description:
012 of the Visible Thoughts series.

I'm not a big napper. I don't like to nap because if I sleep for more than 30 minutes, I'll wake up super groggy, disoriented, and disheveled unless I sleep the whole 6-8 hours. Trust me, it's not a good look. But I just bought a couch for my new place and took a nap on it, and I woke up after an hour with only minor grogginess. I'm so happy with it xD
